default the
default key to achieving this goal is a more integrated approach to health and social care. Bosch support
defaults
default NICE’s new oversight role on social care and welcomes the opportunity to 
defaultmake a submission to the Health Select Committee on the management of long term conditions. 
defaultFor technology to work, it must be embedded in care pathways that are designed for patients with long term conditions. This means managing their conditions 
defaultacross the continuum of care 
default–
default 
defaultat home
default,
default in the community and in clinical setting
